<p>I was trying to implement bloom filter in java but the problem is that the hash functions are returning values in range -10^20  <pre><code>public long APHash(String str) {     long hash = 0xAAAAAAAA;     for(int i = 0; i &lt; str.length(); i++)     {         if ((i &amp; 1) == 0)         {             hash ^= ((hash &lt;&lt; 7) ^ str.charAt(i) * (hash &gt;&gt; 3));         }         else              {             hash ^= (~((hash &lt;&lt; 11) + str.charAt(i) ^ (hash &gt;&gt; 5)));         }     }     return hash; } </code></pre>